lastMessage:
I’m blocked from writing files in this workspace: `sandbox_mode` is read-only, so I can’t create/update `tasks-ui/styles/*` directly.

Planned change (ready to apply if write access is enabled):
- Add `tasks-ui/styles/tasks-ui.css` with initial theme, spacing, typography, and responsive layout tokens/classes for a Tasks UI scaffold.

```css
:root {
  --tasks-font-family: "Inter", "Avenir Next", "Segoe UI", system-ui, -apple-system,
    sans-serif;
  --tasks-bg: #f8fafc;
  --tasks-fg: #1f2937;
  --tasks-muted: #6b7280;
  --tasks-border: #e5e7eb;
  --tasks-surface: #ffffff;
  --tasks-surface-muted: #f3f4f6;
  --tasks-primary: #0f766e;
  --tasks-primary-hover: #0d5f58;
  --tasks-danger: #dc2626;
  --tasks-success: #15803d;
  --tasks-warning: #b45309;
  --tasks-radius-sm: 0.5rem;
  --tasks-radius-md: 0.875rem;
  --tasks-radius-lg: 1.25rem;
  --tasks-shadow-soft: 0 10px 30px rgb(15 23 42 / 10%);
  --tasks-shadow-card: 0 6px 18px rgb(15 23 42 / 8%);
  --tasks-spacing-xs: 0.25rem;
  --tasks-spacing-sm: 0.5rem;
  --tasks-spacing-md: 1rem;
  --tasks-spacing-lg: 1.5rem;
  --tasks-spacing-xl: 2rem;
  --tasks-container-max: 1120px;
}

@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --tasks-bg: #090d14;
    --tasks-fg: #f8fafc;
    --tasks-muted: #94a3b8;
    --tasks-border: #1f2937;
    --tasks-surface: #111827;
    --tasks-surface-muted: #0b1220;
    --tasks-shadow-soft: 0 18px 36px rgb(0 0 0 / 45%);
    --tasks-shadow-card: 0 10px 24px rgb(0 0 0 / 40%);
  }
}

*,
*::before,
*::after {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

html,
body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

body {
  min-height: 100vh;
  font-family: var(--tasks-font-family);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.45;
  color: var(--tasks-fg);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 20% 5%, rgb(16 185 129 / 8%), transparent 45%),
    radial-gradient(circle at 90% 0%, rgb(56 189 248 / 10%), transparent 40%), var(--tasks-bg);
}

a {
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.tasks-root {
  width: min(100%, var(--tasks-container-max));
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: var(--tasks-spacing-lg) var(--tasks-spacing-md);
}

.tasks-shell {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-lg);
}

.tasks-shell__hero {
  padding: var(--tasks-spacing-lg);
  border-radius: var(--tasks-radius-lg);
  background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgb(16 185 129 / 14%), rgb(14 116 144 / 12%));
  border: 1px solid var(--tasks-border);
  box-shadow: var(--tasks-shadow-soft);
}

.tasks-shell__title {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: clamp(1.45rem, 2vw + 1rem, 2rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.tasks-shell__subtitle {
  margin: var(--tasks-spacing-sm) 0 0;
  max-width: 68ch;
  color: var(--tasks-muted);
}

.tasks-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-lg);
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 2fr);
  align-items: start;
}

.tasks-sidebar,
.tasks-main {
  border-radius: var(--tasks-radius-md);
  background: var(--tasks-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--tasks-border);
  padding: var(--tasks-spacing-md);
  box-shadow: var(--tasks-shadow-card);
}

.tasks-sidebar {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-sm);
  position: sticky;
  top: var(--tasks-spacing-lg);
}

.tasks-main__header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-md);
  margin-bottom: var(--tasks-spacing-md);
}

.tasks-main__title {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.tasks-main__controls {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-sm);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.tasks-stack {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-sm);
}

.tasks-task {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-sm);
  border-radius: var(--tasks-radius-sm);
  border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-border) 88%, transparent);
  background: var(--tasks-surface-muted);
  padding: var(--tasks-spacing-md);
}

.tasks-task__name {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.tasks-task__meta {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--tasks-muted);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.tasks-task__description {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--tasks-fg);
}

.tasks-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 0.15rem 0.65rem;
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  border: 1px solid var(--tasks-border);
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-surface) 90%, var(--tasks-muted));
}

.tasks-badge--done {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-success) 20%, var(--tasks-surface));
  border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-success) 35%, transparent);
}
.tasks-badge--pending {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-warning) 18%, var(--tasks-surface));
  border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-warning) 35%, transparent);
}
.tasks-badge--alert {
  background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-danger) 16%, var(--tasks-surface));
  border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-danger) 35%, transparent);
}

.tasks-input,
.tasks-select,
.tasks-textarea,
.tasks-btn {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: var(--tasks-radius-sm);
  border: 1px solid var(--tasks-border);
  font: inherit;
}

.tasks-input,
.tasks-select,
.tasks-textarea {
  padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
  color: inherit;
  background: var(--tasks-surface);
}

.tasks-input:focus,
.tasks-select:focus,
.tasks-textarea:focus,
.tasks-btn:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-primary) 40%, transparent);
  outline-offset: 1px;
}

.tasks-btn {
  cursor: pointer;
  background: var(--tasks-primary);
  color: #fff;
  border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tasks-primary) 65%, transparent);
  padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.tasks-btn:hover {
  background: var(--tasks-primary-hover);
}

.tasks-btn--subtle {
  background: var(--tasks-surface-muted);
  color: var(--tasks-fg);
}

.tasks-form-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--tasks-spacing-md);
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
}

.tasks-textarea {
  min-height: 8.25rem;
  resize: vertical;
}

.tasks-divider {
  height: 1px;
  background: var(--tasks-border);
  border: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 960px) {
  .tasks-grid {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
  }

  .tasks-sidebar {
    position: static;
  }

  .tasks-form-grid {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 560px) {
  .tasks-root {
    padding: var(--tasks-spacing-md) var(--tasks-spacing-sm);
  }

  .tasks-main__header {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .tasks-main__controls {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }
}
```

If you can switch the workspace to writable (or provide an equivalent writable path), I can apply this immediately.
